<div id="focusModal" data-element="yes" class="modal is-large-rounded">
	<div class="modal-background"></div>
	<div class="modal-card">
		<header class="modal-card-head">
			<p class="modal-card-title">Add to focused</p>
			<button id="focusModalCloseButton" data-element="yes" class="delete" aria-label="close"></button>
		</header>
		<section class="modal-card-body">
			<p>Add this position to your focused repertoire.</p>
			<p class="mt-3">In the focused repertoire you can group certain positions together and get a side by side view.</p>
			<p class="mt-3">You can use this for positions that are similar where you are unsure of the move or just for positions you want to put extra focus on.</p>
			<p class="mt-3">The notes will be displayed during practice.</p>
			<div class="field mt-4">
				<label class="label">Notes</label>
				<div class="control">
					<textarea id="focusModalNotesTextarea" data-element="yes" placeholder="Enter optional notes here..." class="textarea"></textarea>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<footer class="modal-card-foot is-justify-content-flex-end">
			<div class="buttons">
				<button id="focusModalCancelButton" data-element="yes" class="button">
					Cancel
				</button>
				<button id="focusModalConfirmButton" data-element="yes" class="button is-warning">
					Confirm
				</button>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</div>
</div>
